Package org.gcn.plinguacore.simulator.cellLike.activeMembranes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActiveMembranesCreateSimulator
    This class creates simulators which comply with Active Membrane model conditions
    ActiveMembranesSimulator
    A simulator for active membrane P systems (with division or creation rules)
    CreationPsystemFactory
    This class is intended to give support for P-systems in which only membrane creation, evolution, dissolution and communication are allowed
    DivisionPsystemFactory
    This class is intended to give support for P-systems in which only membrane division, evolution, dissolution and communication are allowed
